{"tid":2062470,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★財困29歲仔 大埔富亨邨後樓梯墮樓亡","createTime":"2020-06-13T07:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T09:04:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"22c584b67e7667325576390658a2c2d1b5ed4640","tid":2062470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】一名疑受金錢問題困擾的29歲男子，早上在大埔富亨邨一後樓梯墮斃，傳出的巨響驚動保安員報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方早上6時31分接獲保安報案，指聽到一聲巨響，發現事主倒卧亨盛樓對開，懷疑從高處墮下。警員接報到場，事主當場被證實死亡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信從一後樓梯間墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n死者一名男親友到場認屍時情緒激動，跪在屍體旁痛哭。據悉，疑因欠債尋死的事主並非亨盛樓居民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E5%9B%B029%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%8C%E4%BA%A8%E9%82%A8%E5%BE%8C%E6%A8%93%E6%A2%AF%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-035000079.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%259B%25B029%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E5%25AF%258C%25E4%25BA%25A8%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25BA%25A1-035000079.html&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJri2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=d0052466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E5%9B%B029%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%8C%E4%BA%A8%E9%82%A8%E5%BE%8C%E6%A8%93%E6%A2%AF%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-035000079.html</a>"},{"pid":"052da90bd29b51076b307dcf5048cdeef662dbe1","tid":2062470,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"無可疑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7070df033925b6a39c5943e813a905eb41a99940","tid":2062470,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"十成十買左老貓科技啦"},{"pid":"e6c7c240c061f191f6d7f5d266badd16ef2994e0","tid":2062470,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:08:49.000Z","msg":